gold_answer: Assuming the question is about the IBM Cloud® Virtual Private Cloud (VPC) command line interface (CLI),  version 6.15.0 includes the following changes over version 6.14.0. It introduces new commands image-obsolete and image-deprecate for image lifecycle management. It also adds support for image lifecycle management in image-create, image-update, and images commands and it fixes an issue with using the SSH key generated from UI in CLI.

VPC CLI release notes 

The following release notes are for the IBM Cloud® Virtual Private Cloud (VPC) command line interface (CLI).



 v6.15.0 

Version 6.15.0 was released on 2023-07-11.



 New commands 



* New commands image-obsolete and image-deprecate are introduced to support image lifecycle management.







 Updated commands 



* Added support for image lifecycle management in image-create, image-update, and images commands.







 Removed commands 



* N/A







 Notes 



* N/A

 New commands
